Class TarantoolClientConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.tarantool.driver.api.TarantoolClientConfig
  • public class TarantoolClientConfig
extends Object
    Class-container for TarantoolClient configuration.

    It is recommended to use the TarantoolClientConfig.Builder for constructing the configuration
